						<summary>

						<p>This is an inscription of <hi rend="bold">Parāntaka I.</hi> It records a gift of 5 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold by the standard weight) <hi rend="italic">kāseṭṭāngal</hi> for burning a lamp during the day in the temple of Mahādēva at Tirunōmbalūr by <hi rend="bold">Araiyaṉ Kāmaṉ</hi> a resident of <hi rend="bold">Śiṟṟūr</hi> in Mīyamaḻa-nāḍu. </p>						

						</summary>
